metadata.description:
Architectural studies from Caput Mundi, Rome 2136. The historic city still stands, the rich still have palzzos and apartments in renovated historic surroundings authentic - somewhat. But much of Rome has transformed into these city sized dwellings, so all catering to their work and life needs, that the inhabitants might never have a reason to leave.
